    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 16. Minibiotus diversus sp. nov. habitus: 15 — dorsal view; 16 — ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/233665/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.233667>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 – 24. Minibiotus diversus sp. nov.: 19 — pores arranged in rows between legs I and II; 20 — pores on dorsal side; 21 — triangle – like formation of pores on ventral side of head segment; 22 — large pores on frontal side of the body (dorsal view); 23 – 24 — large pores on posterior side of the body (dorsal view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/233667/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.233668>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 29. Minibiotus diversus sp. nov.: 25 – 28 — granulation on legs I – IV; 29 — large pores on external side of the legs II – III (lateral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/233668/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.233666>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 18. Minibiotus diversus sp. nov.: 17 — buccal apparatus (ventral view); 18 — claws IV." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/233666/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.233669>
